addRowElements

public Table<E> addRowElements(Map<String,E> columnToElementMap,
                               boolean createColumnTitleIfDontExists)
Description copied from interface: Table
Adds the values of a given Map as new row to the Table. The keys of the Map are treated as column titles. Any key within the Map which is not available as column title will create a new column with exactly this title if the given createColumnTitleIfDontExists flag is set to true.

Adds the values of a given Map as new row to the Table. The keys of the Map are treated as column titles. Any key within the Map which is not available as column title will create a new column with exactly this title.
